                           <locus from="1va" to="6vb"/>
                           <locus from="126va" to="127va"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Treatise on love to God and people, and on guarding the faith, addressed to monks (unidentified). It has been corrected by a contemporary hand.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">መቅደም፡ ኵሉ፡ አፍቅሮ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ አምላክከ፡ በኵሉ፡ ልብከ፡ ወበኵሉ፡ ነፍስከ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="MK"/></q>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus from="124ra" to="126ra"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText"> 
                              <title ref="LIT5625TergSenaFet">Tǝrgʷāme śǝna fǝṭrat ‘Commentary on the Beauty of
                                 Creation’</title>. The text is written in a hand which is contemporary and similar to
                              <ref target="#h1">Hand 1</ref>. It was  checked for errors and corrected by another hand. For a similar text see manuscripts <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmakm014"/>
                              and <ref type="mss" corresp="ESthmr018"/>.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ትርጓሜ: ኦሪት፡ ብሂል፡ ፍትሕ፡ ወሥርዐት: ወዜና፡ ይትበሃል፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="MK"/></q>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus from="126ra" to="126va"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Excerpt from the <title ref="LIT2709Matthew">Gospel of Matthew</title> (Mt. 5: 1–11).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus from="127va" to="127vb"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Excerpt from <title ref="LIT2736RepCh20" type="incomplete">Malkʾa Śǝllāse (‘Image of the Trinity’)</title>. </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">አልብየ፡ ባእደ፡ ዘእንበሌክሙ፡ አምላከ፤ አብል፡
                              አንሰ፡ በልብየ: ነግሐ: ወሠርከ። ሥሉስ: ቅዱስ፡ ዘአልብክሙ፡ ተውሰከ። በሉኒ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ሰረይነ፡ ለከ፡ ኃጢአተ፡ ኵሎ፡ ዘገበርከ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="MK"/></q>
